<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ١٠١ ... سُورَةُ القَارِعَةِ ... آياتها ١١ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقَارِعَةُ}</span> ... القِيَامَةُ الَّتِي تَقْرَعُ القُلُوبَ بِأَهْوَالِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَبْثُوثِ}</span> ... المُنْتَشِرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالْعِهْنِ}</span> ... كَالصُّوفِ المَصْبُوغِ بِأَلْوَانٍ مُخْتَلِفَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَنفُوشِ}</span> ... الَّذِي مُزِّقَ، وَنُفِشَ، فَتَفَرَّقَتْ أَجْزَاؤُهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثَقُلَتْ مَوَازِينُهُ}</span> ... رَجَحَتْ مَوَازِينُ حَسَنَاتِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأُمُّهُ هَاوِيَةٌ}</span> ... مَاوَاهُ إِلَى جَهَنَّمَ يَهْوِي عَلَى رَاسِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَامِيَةٌ}</span> ... حَارَّةٌ قَدِ اشْتَدَّ إِيقَادُهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>